{"tid":705883,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"原來著住校服cosplay扑野係咁正","createTime":"2018-06-17T14:09:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-12T11:49:27.000Z","uid":99568,"like":7,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"4f41a53ea01cabc2aaf2434c4468aef5639e22d1","tid":705883,"uid":99568,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-17T14:09:24.000Z","msg":"同佢一齊左三年 <br />\n扑野方面真係咩花式都玩過哂 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n呢排覺得自己開始無咩想搞佢既衝動 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但就係尋晚 佢突然話想著住校服比我搞 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我問佢你無啦啦喺邊度攞套校服返嚟， 佢笑笑口面紅紅咁同我講話著番以前中學嗰度咪得囉<br />\n<br />\n佢係衣櫃拎左套校服出黎著左上身 <br />\n我即刻好似撻著左咁撲低左佢 <br />\n<br />\n我:一齊三年而家先知你讀英華<br />\n佢: 嘻嘻 傻豬 <br />\n<br />\n就係咁 <br />\n我地就渡過左激情既夜晚 <br />\n詳細唔多講 <br />\n但我覺得我地既關係已經修補左"},{"pid":"0b2bba7987daf101dd9aef25140919c3501c2eb7","tid":705883,"uid":99568,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-17T14:10:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/17/221001_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F17%2F221001_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=e198e071&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"dfe952bef35f85ecd0b9059b4ec118958228267e","tid":705883,"uid":120070,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-17T14:11:05.000Z","msg":"屌你個標題  你係咪差梗啲野？"},{"pid":"bab03f10befbc8cca56fd42ac4e63202421a1025","tid":705883,"uid":94828,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"dfe952bef35f85ecd0b9059b4ec118958228267e","tid":705883,"uid":120070,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-17T14:11:05.000Z","msg":"屌你個標題  你係咪差梗啲野？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-17T14:12:04.000Z","msg":"英華仔喎 真係要睇？"},{"pid":"94c536a5aa05ad1aeeed035c3aece41e85b26586","tid":705883,"uid":99568,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"